{"type": "article", "id": 9884, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-05-22T08:02:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 1672, "name": "沙发"}, {"id": 7491, "name": "桌面用品"}, {"id": 3704, "name": "鞋子"}, {"id": 1705, "name": "腕表"}, {"id": 10496, "name": "Lujo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135623IvVOEyDGtSQgsa8L.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tBlink by Yabu Pushelberg\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这是 Yabu Pushelberg 为 Stellar Works 推出的系列家具，包括椅子，咖啡桌，边桌、双人沙发、屏风以及不同型号的陈列柜。整个系列采用浅珊瑚和浅灰配色，每件作品都有着憨厚的形态和温柔的线条，营造出甜蜜而轻快的气氛。目前作品正在伦敦克勒肯维尔设计周上进行展出。<a href=\"http://www.clerkenwelldesignweek.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看设计周详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142050FtnIyGZCraBAj703.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142051b8XWMeNrVEJ9ykvF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60880196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142051mpW1FeaRoEHV6dq7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59779951\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071420522nHbQeT60DNraYtj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tHoneycomb Gloss by Adidas Originals \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tAdidas Originals 最近以其经典小白鞋 Stan Smith 为蓝本，新推出了一个叫做 Honeycomb Gloss 的女鞋系列。这一系列作品保留了 Stan Smith 经典的样式，包括简单的轮廓和配色。而不同的是，在材料上这次选用带有蜂窝纹路细节的白色皮革，而不是原来光滑的皮革，看上去细节充实。这个系列产品将于今年 6 月 1 日正式登陆 Adidas Originals 店铺。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142052pEvwa0nzTLxZ6Olj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142053SHO9PiUnT3yWZ568.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142053cbTmGI0VvUZ1pCBS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142054jXGFQghiNOr8ePwR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tNew Botany by Bozka Rydlewska\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t来自华沙的艺术家 Bozka Rydlewska 创作了一个叫做 “New Botany” 的系列 3D 立体限量版书籍。对于植物的热爱源自她童年的记忆。经过长时间的精耕细作，她运用 1：1 的比例模型把植物园中的景象用 3D 立体的形式展现在了我们面前。<a href=\"http://bozka.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是作者的个人网站</a>，点击可以查看她更多作品，同时可以直接联系她沟通购买事宜。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142054y43gJFLrZu08eIfH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142055paMOnirZTkho2SBx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142055hIxM8tmsA23QrR1F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142056Z1ybFpQIkUEluJT9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142056PkKLlUp5x6WAJuXi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142057DlqZosz1kLf53StR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142057PFLpDnOgwGaHe1Bu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tLounge Furniture by Lujo\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t来自新西兰的家居品牌 Lujo 推出了一系列户外家具，包括户外吊床，户外沙发，户外靠垫等。防水和防晒的材料保证产品的质量，黑色，灰色和蓝色的配色设计让整个系列产品看起来简单优雅。如果你有一个露台或是小花园，这是度过一个悠闲的夏日傍晚的好选择。<a href=\"http://lujoliving.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>，他们提供全球送货服务。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142058bzQI4X0moB5FHEuv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142058BChUTvf6GclXqax9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142059P5ZUIvEd9KhLrolq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142059zvILmDVGZBw9sUq5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142059Fy79AKJb6ZQRsgPr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142100T7seL2oVdciQyOq5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142100pdLcQi6N7tROSsuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142101OIgN8DQwk7PdpMKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tNew Collection of Objects by BASE \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t来自旧金山的设计工作室 BASE 推出了一个桌面用品系列，意在提升桌面的整洁度，从而提升工作效率。这个系列包括各种型号的收纳盒，笔筒和烟灰缸等，皆采用 3D 打印形成。材料上选用的聚苯乙烯，配色上所有产品选用整洁的白色，黑色，灰色和橘红色，轮廓简单温柔。产品价格在 35 美元左右，<a href=\"http://base-object.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142101lapUNb75KGd2C6gv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142102SlnGFURdWM0saVpv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142102F6LzkZriCo1T09bY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142103dh46b0aGRt897gUz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142103ka9LKnIbC7x5Qdcp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tFacette by Bulbul \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t丹麦手表品牌 Bulbul 最近推出 Facette 新系列腕表，这个系列采用极简的轮廓和配色设计。材料上采用 4K 镀金机芯和 316L 不锈钢外壳。同时，他们提供六种不同金属表壳。目前产品售价 334 美元，<a href=\"http://www.bulbul.dk/collections/facette\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142104lUxI3X2H8TfP9hRz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142105Fs2pSuHWeIKiYfgr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071421053tqmTAuWgHrRCfhF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142106Nwa3UmnrbPGEehyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72860636\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142106i7UwbGh0cJ4ys6vx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3782235\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142107NlVErtzokY5qeSXA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}